data.name: SqlSelectCommand4.CommandText
data.value: SELECT RTRIM(TB_DOCDOGANALI_BOLLE_IMA.MRN) AS MRN, TB_DOCDOGANALI_BOLLE_IMA_DETTAGLI.MASSANETTA_038, TB_DOCDOGANALI_BOLLE_IMA_DETTAGLI.MASSALORDA_035, RTRIM(TB_ARTICOLI.CODICE) AS CodVermarDM, TB_DOCDOGANALI_BOLLE_IMA_DETTAGLI.ARTICOLINUM_032 AS NumRiga, TB_ARTICOLI.SERIAL AS CodiceDM, TB_DOCDOGANALI_BOLLE_IMA_DETTAGLI.COLLIEMERCI_031_NUM AS Colli, RTRIM(TB_DOCUMENTIDOGANALI.PROGRESSIVO) AS PROGRESSIVO, RTRIM(TB_DOCUMENTIDOGANALI.ALFA) AS ALFA, TB_DOCUMENTIDOGANALI.ANNO, TB_DOCUMENTIDOGANALI.DATA FROM TB_ARTICOLI INNER JOIN TB_MOVMAGAZZINORIGHE ON TB_ARTICOLI.SERIAL = TB_MOVMAGAZZINORIGHE.ARTICOLO INNER JOIN TB_DOCDOGANALI_BOLLE_IMA INNER JOIN TB_DOCDOGANALI_BOLLE_IMA_DETTAGLI ON TB_DOCDOGANALI_BOLLE_IMA.SERIAL = TB_DOCDOGANALI_BOLLE_IMA_DETTAGLI.DOCDOGANALE ON TB_MOVMAGAZZINORIGHE.SERIAL = TB_DOCDOGANALI_BOLLE_IMA_DETTAGLI.MOVMAGAZZINORIGA INNER JOIN TB_DOCUMENTIDOGANALI ON TB_DOCDOGANALI_BOLLE_IMA.DOCDOGANALE = TB_DOCUMENTIDOGANALI.SERIAL WHERE (RTRIM(TB_ARTICOLI.CODICE) LIKE @IdVermar)

data.name: CommMRNuscitiDM.CommandText
data.value: SELECT SUM(MASSANETTA_038) AS NettoExport, SUM(MASSALORDA_035) AS LordoExport, SUM(COLLIEMERCI_031_NUM) AS ColliExport, DOCUMENTOPRECED_040_IDMRN, DOCUMENTOPRECED_040_SINGOLORIFPREC FROM TB_DOCDOGANALI_BOLLE_EX_DETTAGLI GROUP BY DOCUMENTOPRECED_040_IDMRN, DOCUMENTOPRECED_040_SINGOLORIFPREC HAVING (DOCUMENTOPRECED_040_IDMRN = @MRNCarico) AND (DOCUMENTOPRECED_040_SINGOLORIFPREC = @NumItemCarico)

data.name: CommNoMRNUscitiDM.CommandText
data.value: SELECT SUM(MASSANETTA_038) AS NettoExport, SUM(MASSALORDA_035) AS LordoExport, SUM(COLLIEMERCI_031_NUM) AS ColliExport FROM TB_DOCDOGANALI_BOLLE_EX_DETTAGLI WHERE (DOCUMENTOPRECED_040_DATAPREC = @Data) GROUP BY DOCUMENTOPRECED_040_SINGOLORIFPREC, DOCUMENTOPRECED_040_NUMREGISTRAZ, DOCUMENTOPRECED_040_CIN HAVING (DOCUMENTOPRECED_040_SINGOLORIFPREC = @NumItemCarico) AND (DOCUMENTOPRECED_040_NUMREGISTRAZ = @NumDocCarico) AND (DOCUMENTOPRECED_040_CIN = @CIN)
